import React from 'react'
import { Menu } from 'semantic-ui-react';

import User from '.componentes/comp_pagHeader/profile'
import Search from '.componentes/comp_pagHeader/inputSearch'

export default function DefaultHeader() {
    return (
        <Menu>
            <Menu.Menu position="left">
             <Menu.Item>
                {/*<Image size="small" src={logo} circular/>*/}
             </Menu.Item>
            </Menu.Menu>
            <Menu.Menu position="right">
                <Menu.Item>
                    <Search/>

            <Menu.Item>

            </Menu.Item>
            </Menu.Menu>
        </Menu>
    )
}
